Since Terraform v1.1, terraform refresh is deprecated and terraform apply -refresh-only should be used.

terraform apply               → makes infra match code
terraform apply -refresh-only → makes state match real infra

Someone manually added a tag in AWS console
→ terraform apply -refresh-only
→ state file now reflects that manual tag
→ no infra touched

terraform plan -refresh-only   → preview only 👀
terraform apply -refresh-only  → preview + update state ✅

